column1: Baby Barnaby's////Since my first visit I have always ordered the green eggs! It doesn't seem like anything special
column2: but it's just so tasty! The jack cheese mixed with the eggs
column3: spinach and artichoke makes the eggs creamy. The chicken apple sausage isn't too salty
column4: as sometimes it's too salty or smoky for my taste and it has the perfect amount of sweetness to balance out the eggs.
